\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:304:\"If you&#8217;ve tried to import the theme demo on your site and failed then, there might be various reasons for it. And one of them is the PHP configuration of the host server, which could lead to failure of the demo import process. For the demo import process to work properly for your site, we[&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Docs_Manager\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1076:\"\n<p>If you&#8217;ve tried to import the theme demo on your site and failed then, there might be various reasons for it. And one of them is the PHP configuration of the host server, which could lead to failure of the demo import process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the demo import process to work properly for your site, we recommend the following PHP configuration:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>max_execution_time =</strong> 300</li><li><strong>memory_limit</strong> = 256M</li><li><strong>post_max_size</strong> = 32M</li><li><strong>upload_max_filesize</strong> = 32M</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you can change them on your own then, you can set the values as recommended above and try the import after that. However, if you could not then, you can ask your hosting provider to manage those settings as we recommend for demo import.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you&#8217;re on the shared hosting, then, you might not be able to change those values according to the recommendation. So, in this case, you can import the same demo again and again until the demo import comes up as successful.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0: